ResourceInstanceReadTenant.docs: the *key* of the tenant that this resource belongs to, used to enforce tenant boundaries in multi-tenant apps.

ResourceInstanceReadResource.docs: the *key* of the resource (type) of this resource instance. For example: if this resource instance is the annual budget document, the key of the resource might be `document`.

ResourceInstanceReadId.docs: Unique id of the resource instance

ResourceInstanceReadOrganizationId.docs: Unique id of the organization that the resource instance belongs to.

ResourceInstanceReadProjectId.docs: Unique id of the project that the resource instance belongs to.

ResourceInstanceReadEnvironmentId.docs: Unique id of the environment that the resource instance belongs to.

ResourceInstanceReadCreatedAt.docs: Date and time when the resource instance was created (ISO_8601 format).

ResourceInstanceReadUpdatedAt.docs: Date and time when the resource instance was last updated/modified (ISO_8601 format).

ResourceInstanceReadResourceId.docs: the id of the resource (type) of this resource instance.

ResourceInstanceReadTenantId.docs: the id of the tenant of this resource instance.
